text: "Warped" is a 1995 song by Red Hot Chili Peppers and is the leading single from their sixth studio album One Hot Minute. It went to number 3 in Finland, number 4 in New Zealand, number 12 in Australia and Norway, number 14 in the Netherlands and number 31 in the United States. == Track listing == CD single (1995) # "Warped" (edit) # "Pea" (album) # "Melancholy Mechanics" (previously unreleased) == References == Category:1995 songs Category:Red Hot Chili Peppers songs Category:Funk rock songs Category:Hard rock songs
